abstract = "Tate RL, Pfaff A, Veerabangsa A, Hodgkinson AE. Measuring psychosocial recovery after brain injury: change versus competency. Arch Phys Med Rehabil 2004;85:538–45.
Objectives
To determine the psychometric properties of an alternative form of the Sydney Psychosocial Reintegration Scale (SPRS) that focuses on competency of functioning (Form B) as opposed to the original form that examines change from the premorbid level (Form A).
